snippet.title: Super vs World - Major Update 1.3
snippet.description:
Trailer for Super vs World Game Major Update 1.3

Super vs. World is a local-multiplayer 2D versus party game that lets up to 8 players combat each other and AI’s with classic headstomping, brick breaking, weapon throwing gameplay!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1451800/Super_vs_World/
